These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
City: miami, nizza, london, rome, colone, berlin
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, house, jazz, r&b, rock, soul
 1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 3. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
 4. the fan of soul is not to the left of the person traveling to london##8
 5. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the fan of rock##5
 6. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the person traveling to berlin##7
 7. the person traveling to miami is not to the left of the fan of jazz##8
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
10. the fan of classical is not to the left of the person traveling to rome##8
11. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
12. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
13. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
14. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere between the fan of house and the person traveling to london##7
15. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
16. the person traveling to colone is not the fan of r&b##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| City           | rome | nizza | miami | colone | berlin | london |
| Music-Genre   | classical | jazz    | house  | rock  | r&b            | soul  |

