.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, fanta, milk, lemonade, iced-tea
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, mouse, pony, turtle
 1. the person drinking milk is not the owner of the turtle##6
 2. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
 3. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the owner of the turtle is between the person drinking milk and the owner of the goat##2
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 8. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the owner of the mouse##6
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
12. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
13. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
14. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
15. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Beverage   | fanta | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | lemonade | milk | almond-milk |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla  | goat         | turtle | pony    | mouse   |

