 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 2. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
 5. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 6. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person watching mystery movies##5
 8. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person watching romance movies##8
 9. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching mystery movies##5
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person watching scientific movies and the person who's sport is cricket##7
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
13. the person watching family movies is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
14. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
15. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person watching spy movies##7
16. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
17. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
18. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
19. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person watching spy movies##6

