 3. the person who likes ebony is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who likes lavender##2
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes ebony is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who likes ebony##8
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
10. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who likes ebony##7
13. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
14. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
15. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
16. the person who likes coral is in an even position##4
17. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5

.:: Answer ::.
