 2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 4. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person traveling to colone##7
 5. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person traveling to hannover is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
 7. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
 8. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
10. the owner of the horse is not the person traveling to new-york##6
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
13. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| City   | colone | rome | edinburgh  | hannover     | marseilles | new-york |
| Pet           | cat        | goat    | turtle | chinchilla | horse     | hamster  |

